{"tid":739362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美促請世貿審視中國成員資格","createTime":"2018-07-12T05:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T01:29:52.000Z","uid":53379,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"77479335c278d6fc90e63550a031bc416eb4854d","tid":739362,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:00:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美促請世貿審視中國成員資格</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中美貿易戰持續升級，美國宣布對總值二千億美元中國進口貨品追加額外關稅後，再要求世界貿易組織審視中國的成員資格，中國批評美國的行為是貿易欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n世貿正對中國進行第七次例行貿易政策審議，中國商務部副部長王受文強調，中國一直持續並大幅自主降低進口關稅稅率，將外商投資限制措施由原來63條減少至48條。<br />\n<br />\n不過美國駐世貿大使謝伊批評，中國無落實自由貿易原則，藉世貿成員國資格佔其他國家便宜，造成嚴重傷害，促請世貿審視中國的成員資格。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=312723&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D312723%26refer%3D&d=HtNzjlSW6o2zHjPDy%2Fl7aDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2511b7e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D312723%26refer%3D&h=567b5fdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=312723&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"2801706be0738bd4604ffdd89b1e08ddf2fe7ad0","tid":739362,"uid":511,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"將外商投資限制措施由原來63條減少至48條。<br />\n<br />\n減咁多，貿易一定好自由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係唔怪之得侵唔玩TPP, TTIP啦，搞咁多個組織做咩春，直接踢支共出WTO仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62f7f2c5100c6de3de35a74d8bdd57f292034b6","tid":739362,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a681d73d9b60b518c5348339d169657bfb24d12","tid":739362,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl